<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٢٣٥٤ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6952">يَحْيَى بْنُ بُكَيْرٍ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5348">اللَّيْثُ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4444">عُقَيْلٍ، </a>عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5917">ابْنِ شِهَابٍ، </a>عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2436">ابْنِ المُسَيَّبِ</a> <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3745">وَأَبِي سَلَمَةَ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3320">أَبِي هُرَيْرَةَ </a><span class="special">﵁</span>: أَنَّ رَسُولَ اللهِ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> قَالَ: <span class="c2">«لَا تَمْنَعُوا فَضْلَ الْمَاءِ لِتَمْنَعُوا بِهِ فَضْلَ الْكَلَإِ.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>